Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好 我是井浦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,比起味增味 我更喜欢盐味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大家喜欢哪种类型的电影呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,科幻片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,比如近未来之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爱情片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是老电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,总而言之 搞笑就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉是有可爱的动物出场的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学不是喜欢猎奇向的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就是会出很多血的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,堀桑和宫村君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,回去还要准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:00:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,去买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:00:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真觉得热得快融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不过实际上也融化不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候啊 我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是堀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 搭讪？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 现在正要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,来的正是时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才看到堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,顺势就上来打个招呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别在我视线里出现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就靠网购活着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 以前我们不是死党吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就帮忙介绍一下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,进藤 高二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,原来的同学 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说得像搜索关键宇一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是宫村的死党进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这家伙的事情 我全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,初三时候的身高是158CM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,体重44KG 视力双眼1.0
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢的女生是隔壁班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心 去死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是个笨蛋 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不 也不能说是笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是八阪高中的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只是学校而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但实际上就是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,太严格了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和中学同学说话是那种感觉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和透也这样试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,「这家伙 你个混蛋」这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,像往常一样的漠不关心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,毫不掩饰的无视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,「宫村还在啊」这样的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,老师说去理科室上课
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么会这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,进藤 给我抄一下试验的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,才不管你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你不去上课吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘记带笔记本了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快要上课了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快点吧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,山村？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 山本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,错得更离谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,山川？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是「山」开头的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是「川」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不是「山」就是「川」这也太单纯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那么有带「桥」字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没带啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来就是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别骗人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快去理科室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我来做课题…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有课题要做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,空调坏了 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我不怎么怕热
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:05:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然睡觉的时候不穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有穿最基本的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为这很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,男生都是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,话说这人动不动就要脱衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,能给我看一下刺青吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别脱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你给我看一下就脱衣服 你这想法太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村你那么容易就在人面前脱衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在透的面前呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在透的面前脱衣服 他会心跳加速吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你得看情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学 我问清楚一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为宫村好像不怎么害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在想 在什么状况下你才会害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得一直是我慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 我刚刚应该害羞对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了 再做一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是觉得热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你觉得别人对我怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了什么都无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,之前碰见进藤的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没有用名来称呼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是你女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学不是我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她受欢迎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好像偶尔还会有人告白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样不行啊 要好好地抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我在担心你会不会被好不容易交上的女朋友甩了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真正想说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请把她的朋友介绍给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果被错以为你是我女朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,进藤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我会好好地告诉他不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,倒也没有否定的必要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我交到女朋友了可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说好了下次和宫村四人一起去玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都做好避孕的准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 这不让我很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别…别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用敬语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我还完全不了解宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你要好好躺着休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要去学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐可不想变成笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说夏天不会感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不是感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没有感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要毛巾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,宝矿力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你怎么在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,创太打电话给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么「姐姐快死了」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿宝矿力来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿饮料…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,躺着要好一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,总是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,京子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你要说的不是「你要去哪里」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而是「不要走」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,用似乎明白的语气问你 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪里也不会去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,「我才不要你在呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,「我更不想看到你」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,「快离开这里」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只要堀同学不这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我就一直在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好…难受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…堀同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我和学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说和石川说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还有就是明天的补习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,听说三年级不用去也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很早以前就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,还有冰箱里放了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有事情就打电话给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要和注意事项一起说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这么重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然想要好好地确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不想让他再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,伊澄君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,伊澄君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,伊澄…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢 我是在叫你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 不是女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说了很多次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要找我来商量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,石川君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,石川君是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么告白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,「我喜欢你！」这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想听到回复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只是随口说了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我很卑鄙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这还挺直接的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至有些过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你想和堀同学怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,想要整天都粘在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,想要挽着胳膊散步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想要向大家炫耀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,想要她对你说「我喜欢你」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想要找她麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不想被任何人夺走她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想要把她藏在箱子里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想要亲她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,想要和她做爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这可是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是想和她做这些事情才告白的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实不想让人夺走她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我能说说你不喜欢听的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是女生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会想和宫村交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,阴暗又不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,初中的时候也被很多人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而且学习也不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,成绩中等偏下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,假设堀同学是像太阳一般的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她周围总有很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,又聪明又有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在班里非常受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,和我这样的人交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为说了是对堀同学好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你在否定自己的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也在否定堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要简单地说出会让喜欢的人伤心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,晃一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是读了两次二年级的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…你不要说这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学今天也请假吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 她好像还有点不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 真的只是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是她朋友 所以我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,千佳 没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村君？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,宫村君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样请假下去的话就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚我看到哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个女人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,贴得超紧 手也挽起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 堀同学来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但好像不想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我要早点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候醒着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和你挽着手一起走的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你是说千佳酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,千佳酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 八阪高中的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次听你叫女生的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,还挽着手在街上走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我和千佳酱不是那样的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,进藤 进藤的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,千佳酱…千佳酱的脚扭到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,进藤他…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在停单车的时候 借了一下肩膀给她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我和千佳酱没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说 千佳…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,千佳千佳千佳千佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好烦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,超性急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,暴力 不讲道理 好大力气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,完全被愤怒支配了行为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经不是鼓起勇气或者确认的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然朝他脸上扔了教科书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这次真的要完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他说我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我用这些书…还扔了你两次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,到底来说 我和千…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
