Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,千佳酱的姓是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这张沙发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是一个人的专座
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,最近完全没有见到他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我醒着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
